{
  "name": "ClickIn360 Onboarding C \u2014 Advocacy",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Self-hosted n8n Community Edition\n\n**No Settings \u2192 Variables** on the free plan. Edit the **Config: Edit These Values** Set node (yellow fields) in each workflow instead.\n\nOptional: you can also set OS/Docker env vars on the n8n container \u2014 not required if you use the Config node.\n\n**NOT the CRM manual Request review button** \u2014 this is automatic on onboarding.complete.\n\nEdit Config: `google_reviews_url` (same as CRM Settings \u2192 Google review invitations).",
